description: Tyler Alexander"The Assassin"Ht: 6'0" WT: 165lbs Season W/L record (0-0)Rod Daily"The Real Deal"Ht: 5'11" WT: 180lbsSeason W/L record (2-0)Welcome to the first installment of Naked Kombat's 10-Man Kombatant Summer Smackdown! Returning to the mat for the first time this season is Tyler "The Assassin" Alexander. Tyler says he's been doing some triathlon training to prepare for the match, and with his background of wrestling and brazilian jiu-jitsu, he says he'll have no problem taking his oversized monkey of an opponent down. Rod "The Real Deal" Daily returns after a back to back win with an undefeated record. Rod also has a background of wrestling and jiu-jitsu and he says he's going to prove to his opponent that he's no match for this tournament by pounding his ass till The Assassin can't take anymore. Their eyes are fixed on winning the gold belt as they hold nothing back fighting balls to the wall for anything in favor to keep them from getting fucked. Which kombatant will move one step closer to being crowned champion while the other is eliminated from the tournament, fucked and defeated?
title: First Match of NK's Summer Smackdown 10-Man Kombatant Tournament!
